<div class="title">Conveniently Subtle</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2 & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Merlin&Exact=1">Merlin</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Merlin. "Conveniently Subtle: An Experience with 2C-T-2 & Cannabis (exp29990)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 14, 2004. erowid.org/exp/29990</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
